{"word":"χειμερινός","slug":"χειμερινός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>χειμερινός</b></el> <el>(χειμερῐνός, ή, όν) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:χεῖμα'><el>χεῖμα</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>of</i> or <i>in winter, of</i> or <i>in winter-time</i>, <a href='S:opposed to'>opp. to</a> <el>θερινός, χ. τροπαί</el> (<a href='S:vide'>v.</a> <a href='S:τροπή'><el>τροπή</el></a> 1), <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <el>τὴν χ.</el> (<a href='S:scilicet'>sc.</a> <el>ὥρην</el>) <i>during the winter season</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>wintry</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>; <a href='S:vide'>v.</a> <el>χειμέριος.</el><p/></div>"}]}